      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to serve as a reliable daily driver. The exterior exhibits some signs of use, including a few minor door dings, surface scratches, and some fading on the trim pieces. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though all major electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may benefit from a routine service in the near future to ensure continued reliability. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for practical transportation at a reasonable price point.",
