      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and driven very gently. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust. It runs like a dream and is ready for your next big road trip! Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
