      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine, showroom-quality example that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior features original, high-gloss paint completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the interior still retains that 'new car' scent with leather that is supple and entirely free of wear. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history documenting its life in a climate-controlled garage. Having never seen rain or salt, the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare find for a collector or a buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection.",
